snippet.title: Sticky Business Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Create, pack, and sell your own unique sticker creations in Sticky Business! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2303350/Sticky_Business/
🎨 Thousands of unique combinations
✂️ Build the perfect sheets to get the most out of your resources
📦 Pack orders for your customers and hear about their lives
✨Unlock new graphics and foil effects
#indiegames #stickers #cozygames
